{"uuid": "f27823bf-387b-4c5d-9e7d-b384938b65bf", "id": 55845, "date": "2025-02-02T04:00:03", "date_gmt": "2025-02-02T12:00:03", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=55845"}, "modified": "2025-11-24T14:49:28", "modified_gmt": "2025-11-24T22:49:28", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-february-2-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/02/02/kingdom-of-days-february-2-2/", "title": {"rendered": "February 2"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>Ten days after Steel Mill plays their final show, Bruce is already in the market for talent for a new band. This help wanted ad runs in the <em>Asbury Park Press\u00a0</em>today.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"63616\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/02/02/kingdom-of-days-february-2-2/asbury_park_press_1971_02_02_page_29/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Asbury_Park_Press_1971_02_02_Page_29-scaled.jpg?fit=2560%2C1683&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2560,1683\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Asbury_Park_Press_1971_02_02_Page_29\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Asbury_Park_Press_1971_02_02_Page_29-scaled.jpg?fit=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Asbury_Park_Press_1971_02_02_Page_29-scaled.jpg?fit=758%2C498&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-63616\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Asbury_Park_Press_1971_02_02_Page_29.jpg?w=758&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1973:</strong> Bruce and the as yet unnamed E Street Band play their third of six nights at Max&#8217;s Kansas City in New York. <span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">(photo credit: Chuck Pulin)</span></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"424\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1973-0202/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1973-0202.jpg?fit=194%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"194,300\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1973-0202\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1973-0202.jpg?fit=194%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1973-0202.jpg?fit=194%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"wp-image-424 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1973-0202-194x300.jpg?resize=758%2C1172\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1172\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1974:</strong> Bruce and the band headline at Springfield College, where a snowstorm keeps all but about 30 people from attending. When the power goes out during the show, Bruce switches to solo piano.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"425\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-0202/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1974-0202.jpg?fit=600%2C363&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"600,363\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-0202\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1974-0202.jpg?fit=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1974-0202.jpg?fit=600%2C363&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-425 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1974-0202-300x182.jpg?resize=758%2C460\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"460\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1974-0202.jpg?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1974-0202.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>The River Tour (original version) moves on to Dane County Memorial Coliseum in Madison, Wisconsin.</p>\n<div id=\"v-Aj2vCNPN-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Aj2vCNPN?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"15813\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-02-02/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1981-02-02.jpg?fit=1617%2C804&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1617,804\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1579980459&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-02-02\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1981-02-02.jpg?fit=300%2C149&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1981-02-02.jpg?fit=758%2C377&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-15813 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1981-02-02-300x149.jpg?resize=758%2C376\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1981-02-02.jpg?resize=300%2C149&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1981-02-02.jpg?resize=1024%2C509&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1981-02-02.jpg?resize=768%2C382&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1981-02-02.jpg?resize=1536%2C764&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1981-02-02.jpg?w=1617&amp;ssl=1 1617w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"426\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-0202/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1981-0202.jpg?fit=1012%2C590&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1012,590\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Picasa&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1335130527&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-0202\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1981-0202.jpg?fit=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1981-0202.jpg?fit=758%2C442&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-426 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1981-0202-300x175.jpg?resize=758%2C442\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1981-0202.jpg?resize=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1981-0202.jpg?resize=768%2C448&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1981-0202.jpg?w=1012&amp;ssl=1 1012w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1987:</strong>\u00a0<em>Live 1975-85\u00a0</em>is certified 3x Platinum by the Recording Industry Association of America.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen &amp; The E Street Band Live 1975-85\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=OLAK5uy_mrHx1dve8r_KqMzbDiKhgcMG0DUjSOcb4\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band rehearse for their upcoming Tunnel of Love Express Tour at the Expo Theater in Fort Monmouth, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><strong>1992:</strong> Bruce and Patti are in New Orleans filming the video for &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/08/09/roll-of-the-dice-human-touch/\">Human Touch</a>.&#8221; That evening, they drop by the Maple Leaf Bar, where the Iguanas are playing. Introduced by a pseudonym, Bruce joins the band for &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/03/08/meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-beaver-brown-aint-that-a-shame/\">Ain&#8217;t That a Shame,</a>&#8221; &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/10/25/cover-me-save-the-last-dance-for-me/\">Save the Last Dance for Me</a>&#8221; and &#8220;Betty Jean.&#8221;</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"63537\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/02/02/kingdom-of-days-february-2-2/the_toronto_star_1992_02_27_43/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The_Toronto_Star_1992_02_27_43-scaled.jpg?fit=2225%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2225,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"The_Toronto_Star_1992_02_27_43\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The_Toronto_Star_1992_02_27_43-scaled.jpg?fit=261%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The_Toronto_Star_1992_02_27_43-scaled.jpg?fit=758%2C872&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-63537\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/The_Toronto_Star_1992_02_27_43.jpg?w=758&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>The River Tour (2016 edition) makes a single stop in Canada, at the Air Center in Toronto.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen   Hungry Heart  Toronto 2016\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2WG7ZnXv7uM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - The River   (Live Toronto Feb 2/16)\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mPbhxKkHPo0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen the E Street Band 2/2/16 Toronto I&#039;m a Rocker Air Canada Centre\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8MNJ0YuGkio?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen and the E Street Band  Promised Land Toronto 2/2/16 Air Canada Centre\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DV8DeHYFgcw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - Thunder Road (Toronto 2016)\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XyF69cUZcP4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>2017</strong>: The Australian Summer Tour moves to Melbourne. Finding it embarrassing to represent America during the early days of the Trump Administration, Bruce makes a statement by opening with an acoustic cover of The Orlon&#8217;s &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/05/13/cover-me-dont-hang-up/\">Don&#8217;t Hang Up</a>,&#8221; dedicated to Prime Minister Turnbull after Trump hung up on their call the previous day. Bruce follows up with &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/01/10/roll-of-the-dice-american-land/\">American Land</a>&#8221; and also includes a solo acoustic &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/03/21/roll-of-the-dice-long-walk-home/\">Long Walk Home</a>&#8221; in the encores, bookending the show with pointed statements.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"&quot;Don&#039;t Hang Up&quot; (Melbourne, 02/02/17)\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zSiZMyUlw8Y?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen - Melbourne, AAMI Park - Glory Days - 2017-02-04\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/C3W1W1cv4JM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"I&#039;m On Fire  - Bruce Springsteen - Melbourne AAMI Stadium - 2nd February 2017\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/evJ40vieXQ4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"2017-02-02 - Bruce Springsteen - Melbourne, AAMI Park - Long Walk Home\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Juk0Y_9lrCY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"24774\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2017-02-02/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2017-02-02.png?fit=1267%2C1125&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1267,1125\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2017-02-02\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2017-02-02.png?fit=300%2C266&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2017-02-02.png?fit=758%2C673&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-24774\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2017-02-02.png?resize=758%2C672&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"672\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2017-02-02.png?resize=300%2C266&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2017-02-02.png?resize=1024%2C909&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2017-02-02.png?resize=768%2C682&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2017-02-02.png?w=1267&amp;ssl=1 1267w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2024:\u00a0</strong>Bruce salutes and performs with Jon Bon Jovi at the annual MusiCares Person of the Year gala in honor of Bon Jovi. The two perform &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/06/22/matr-jon-bon-jovi-and-bruce-springsteen-who-says-you-cant-go-home/\">Who Says You Can&#8217;t Go Home</a>&#8221; and &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/07/04/roll-of-the-dice-the-promised-land/\">The Promised Land</a>&#8221; together.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Jon Bon Jovi And B